<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmed - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .confirmation-badge {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            color: #155724;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .contact-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .contact-card {
            background-color: #e8f4f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .important-note {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üìã Booking Confirmed!</h1>
        <p>Your shipment has been successfully booked</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="confirmation-badge">
            <h2>‚úÖ Booking Confirmed</h2>
            <p>Booking ID: <strong>#<%= bookingId %></strong></p>
            <p>Your shipment is now scheduled and ready for pickup!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="booking-details">
            <h3>üì¶ Shipment Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
            <p><strong>Final Amount:</strong> ‚Ç¶<%= finalAmount %></p>
            <p><strong>Pickup Date:</strong> <%= pickupTime %></p>
            <p><strong>Delivery Date:</strong> <%= deliveryTime %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info">
            <div class="contact-card">
                <h4>üì§ Shipper Information</h4>
                <p><strong>Company:</strong> <%= shipperCompany %></p>
                <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= shipperContact %></p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= shipperPhone %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-card">
                <h4>üöõ Carrier Information</h4>
                <p><strong>Company:</strong> <%= carrierCompany %></p>
                <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= carrierContact %></p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= carrierPhone %></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <center>
            <a href="<%= bookingUrl %>" class="button">View Full Booking Details</a>
        </center>
        
        <div class="important-note">
            <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Next Steps</h3>
            <p><strong>For Shippers:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Prepare your cargo for pickup at the scheduled time</li>
                <li>Ensure all necessary documentation is ready</li>
                <li>Have the agreed payment method ready</li>
                <li>Coordinate with the carrier for exact pickup location</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>For Carriers:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Confirm your truck is ready and available</li>
                <li>Contact the shipper to confirm pickup details</li>
                <li>Ensure all required permits and documentation are in order</li>
                <li>Arrive at the pickup location on time</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>üì± Track Your Shipment</strong></p>
        <p>You can track the progress of your shipment in real-time through your IpTruck dashboard. Both shipper and carrier will receive updates throughout the journey.</p>
        
        <p><strong>üí¨ Communication</strong></p>
        <p>Use the IpTruck messaging system to communicate directly with each other regarding any updates or changes to the shipment.</p>
        
        <p><strong>üÜò Need Help?</strong></p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is available 24/7 at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a> or through the help center in your dashboard.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing IpTruck for your logistics needs. We're committed to making your shipping experience smooth and reliable!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The IpTruck Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You received this email because a booking was confirmed involving your account.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
